Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:01.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.72,0:00:03.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:05.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time, their\ndestinies are controlled by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A detestable demon appears!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I love pork cutlets,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I refuse to become\na demon's bride!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But things didn't turn\nout quite the way I expected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the first time in ages,\NI went home to the present.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I was taking part in\nthe Cultural Festival,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we ended up having to put\ndown several demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a time it was!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:19.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuya-I mean, Pekopon!\NDo something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't need to\nsay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, it was time to\nreturn to the Feudal Era.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to do our best to\nfind the remaining shards{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the Shikon Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father....Mother....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tonight I will have\nto leave {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:55.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We're all\ngoing to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:59.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could I give my daughter\nto marry a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lovely bride!\NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How {\i1}lovely....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:44.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My dear {\i1}girl....{\i0} Will you\nbear my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then come, my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:22.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? A demon who\nsteals young girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You see, our shrine was demolished\nby a band of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,as they came flying through,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the demon which had been sealed\ninside was set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demon, whenever he sees\na beautiful, young girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:42.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he asks if she will bear\nhis child and then abducts her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's atrocious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanting them to have his babies!\NHow dare he!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those villages that refused him\nwere thoroughly destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a despicable being!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'd love to help you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but we have the remaining\njewel shards yet to {\i1}find....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we can't just leave\nthem like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those demons appeared because\nof Mt. Hakurei, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, is there no one\nwho will help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's up to me.\NI'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can take care of the little snits\nand be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure if Inuyasha goes,\nthere'll be no problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:35.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't leave our beautiful maidens\nin the cave forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've gotten all the lovely girls\nfrom the surrounding areas
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:44.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and put them into a cave\nwhere the demon can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd worry if Inuyasha\ngoes all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you're going, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:56.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm also worried\nabout the young girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but not for the reason\NKisuke {\i1}mentioned....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede! We'll\nbe back in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They all ended up going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:19.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon only goes after\nyoung, single girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....?{\i0} Young? Single?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- We have to stay on our toes.\N- Don't worry. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is Sango all\nworked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:34.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're as clueless as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:40.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There it is!\NIt's that cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kisuke!!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everybody! Kisuke has returned\nwith help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kisuke!\N- How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Thank goodness he's back!\N- We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everybody! You can relax now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've brought these experts\nat killing demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Thank goodness!\N- I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can trust these\nfolks completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup! Except their {\i1}character....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was speaking of {\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On the way over here\NI thought of a strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to keep the demon from\nchoosing you all as brides.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is. Just {\i1}one....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:35.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon only chooses\nsingle girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In that {\i1}case....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:43.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miss? Will you have my baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:48.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then the demon won't want you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:51.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monk....!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:52.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That joke isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:01.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demonic aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no! He may have\nfound this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this guy was the cause of\nthe presence I've been {\i1}feeling....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He stinks of a wild beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Miroku? Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- And then me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, this is to ensure\na safe {\i1}delivery....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You girls can't believe\neverything you hear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't let the girls come outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demon wields a huge spear\nand is very fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm dying to get a look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get far from the girls' cave\nand go out to meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he's a beast, won't he be\nable to smell the girls out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In that case, he'd be drawn by\nthe smell of Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! But since the demon only\ngoes after young, pretty girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll let you off this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Young and pretty? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Idiots never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:27.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you given up and brought\nme a bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That must be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:47.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You? You're the demon who's\nlooking for wives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:52.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right! Young lady,\nwould you like to bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I've heard that\nbefore {\i1}somewhere....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez! What a letdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought he was a\nmuch scarier demon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:07.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I'd be able to have some fun\nfor the first time in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A pig {\i1}demon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not a pig!\NI'm a wild boar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:17.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, clearly they don't need me.\NInuyasha, you handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! Do what\nyou like with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, would you, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You two!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:27.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fearing my power and running off\nwith their tails between their legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You wish! It's because you look\nreally weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How you underestimate the\nthe power of Chokyukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chokyukai? I've heard that name\nsomewhere {\i1}before....or{\i0} have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I like pork cutlets but\NI don't have any pig friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not a pig! A boar!\NNow listen and be amazed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This fellow here is a descendant\nof Sagojo, the great water demon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,from the ancient epic tale from the\ncontinent, "The Journey to the West."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one is a descendant of\nthe Heavenly Saint, Son Goku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I am Chokyukai,\ndescended from Chohakkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the General of the\NArmy of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too impressed even to speak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I've taken a lesson\nfrom my ancestor, Chohakkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and decided to marry\na human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the swine talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! You've never heard\nof "The Journey to the West"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you're really descended from\NChohakkai, in the "Journey to the West"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no clue what\nhe's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I should've known Kagome\nwould know. She's so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Young Miss? You seem to have\nheard of my ancestor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The Journey to the West" is\na famous Chinese epic tale
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of the monk, Sanzo, who makes\nfriends with three demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a monkey, a water sprite\nand a {\i1}pig....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and together they go to India to\nretrieve the holy sutras.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you do know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you! I like pork cutlets on rice\nbut I don't know any pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know all about my ancestor!\NWhat a fine girl you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I'll make you my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:19.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When a girl says, "no," she\nfrequently means, "yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:24.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make you mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I like pork roasts,\nbut no thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that you keep saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, this is getting {\i1}tiresome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:36.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is\nacting {\i1}strangely....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ugh! Don't tell me\nhe's your type!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not what the problem is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something funny about\nthat golden diadem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yow! It's tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:22.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You nearly volunteered\nto become Chokyukai's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:23.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When placed upon\na girl's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this diadem has the power\nto make her fall in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I place it on\na girl's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can make her love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!\NForget it, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:43.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, it doesn't make the wearer\nfall in love with the one that placed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:51.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyone wearing it falls\nin love with Chokyukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, enough fun for one {\i1}day....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:13:59.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:05.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, my dear, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! {\i1}Kagome....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Master....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You still want to interfere?!\NSon Goku! Sagojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grrrrrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, the mongrel's not too {\i1}bad....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:03.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've had enough of you!\NI'll knock you all back to the continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time for you to run off with\nyour tail between your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up, Pig Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you! I'm a boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:16.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll beat you to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:36.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, now that I have my bride,\NI'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:10.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've brought all of you\na new companion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:16.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll sit at the head of the table.\NYou're worthy of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0} Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:27.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn....{\i0} About now, Kagome {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! I was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, this is no time to\nget all depressed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. That one is a demon\nfrom the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's possible our methods of\neradication won't work on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:54.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have here a sutra with prayers\nfrom the continent on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We could try using {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how are we going\nto find his lair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Easy. Just follow his scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But with Kagome in\nthe enemy's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we can't be too aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:12.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a strategy.\NShippo, come listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:22.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's an idea! I hadn't\nthought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll need everyone\nworking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yep, I've gotta keep it\ntogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:41.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My, my! What a fine\nnight this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone dance for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A female voice like\nthe tinkling of bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you need,\ntraveling woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've lost my way and\nam in a difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I could ask to spend\nthe night {\i1}here....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One night or a thousand nights!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come, show me your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am too {\i1}shy....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez, this is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:36.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My, my, my!\NYou're just my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you bear my child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like he hasn't {\i1}noticed....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Either that or he has really\nstrange {\i1}tastes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, we shouldn't be\nstanding outside talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry it up, Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you\ntrembling with joy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine! Then I'll\ntremble with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This... is... about...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I can take!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this? You were with\nthat dog bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snap out of it, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:35.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You all tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good job, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:42.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you have my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, Inuyasha! Give that\nsutra to Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a prayer from the continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:02.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrap it around your\narrow, and shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:17.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not a bad pike\nfor a pig to wield.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You ain't seen nothing yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you wanna challenge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:33.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat am I {\i1}feeling....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Not that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shouldn't toy with\na woman's affections!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:12.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! I let that\nswine get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:15.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he won't be causing\nanymore trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm glad we were able\nto rescue everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, aren't we, Miro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ladies, would you\nbear my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That monk! He's talking\njust like that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suspicious....{\i0} Do you think\nhe's one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:39.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Come on! Say something!\N- Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Girls!\NIs everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone! It's Kisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, clearly he's not popular\nenough to cause us {\i1}worry....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:54.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- It was so frightening!\N- Thank you, Kisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That pig demon\nwas really disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That monk, {\i1}too....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:48.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Little baby foxes look up to\NShippo as their master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:53.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are our leader,\NBoss Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:55.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master, train us\nto become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:57.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have secret techniques, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.36,0:23:59.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean the fox demon technique\nof the Smashing Top?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:00.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something more amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:01.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could they mean\nthat trick Inuyasha uses?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Shippo's New Technique,\NThe Heart Scar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.40,0:24:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my tragic\nlove story.
